<Title>Electronic Engine Controls (EEC) Normal Mode</Title>
<MELSubItem itemNbr="73-21-01-02">
<Title>
<?FTID-xref 1288266.2-73-21-01?>GE</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Normal (NORM) mode may be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Autothrottle system operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Turbine case cooling air flow systems operate normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Both engines are operated in the alternate (ALTN) mode.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Appropriate performance adjustments are applied.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
<?FTID-rev deleted highlight="Deleted NOTE"?>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Note>
<Para> Derated or reduced thrust takeoffs are not allowed.</Para>
</Note>
<Note rev:revStatus="R" rev:revHighlight="Updated NOTE">
<?FTID-rev start?>
<Para>Climb thrust derates are not allowed</Para>
<?FTID-rev end?>
</Note>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Base performance on EECs operating in alternate mode.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para rev:revStatus="R">Use OPT to determine performance weight without impacted MEL(do not select impacted MEL in OPT). <?FTID-rev start?>Then directly reduce performance limited  <?FTID-rev end?><?FTID-rev start?>weights as follows: <?FTID-rev end?></Para>
